'''美国驻古巴大使馆'''（{{lang-en|Embassy of the United States of America in Havana}}、{{lang-es|Embajada de los Estados Unidos de América en La Habana}}）是[[美国|美国]]在[[古巴共和国|古巴共和国]]设立的[[美国驻外机构列表|外交机构]]。两国政府于20世纪60年代到21世纪10年代初间并没有直接的双边外交关系<ref>[http://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/united-states-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-cuba United States severs diplomatic relations with Cuba] {{Wayback|url=http://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/united-states-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-cuba |date=20181129085104 }} History.</ref>。1961年1月3日，20世纪50年代的[[古巴革命|古巴革命]]过后，时任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[德怀特·艾森豪威尔|德怀特·艾森豪威尔]]切断两国关系。两国关系于2015年7月20日由[[古巴共产党|古巴共产党]]第一书记[[劳尔·卡斯特罗|劳尔·卡斯特罗]]和美国总统[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]宣布正常化<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/obama-moves-end-cuban-embargo|title=Obama moves to restore relations with Cuba|date=2014-12-17|publisher=MSNBC|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701090723/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/obama-moves-end-cuban-embargo|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2014/12/17/obama-cuba-alan-gross-prisoner/20526497/|title=Obama opens doors to Cuba after 56 years|date=2014-12-17|newspaper=USA Today|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150606102050/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2014/12/17/obama-cuba-alan-gross-prisoner/20526497/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/18/us-cuba-usa-gross-idUSKBN0JV1H520141218|title=U.S., Cuba restore ties after 50 years|date=2014-12-18|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702231233/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/18/us-cuba-usa-gross-idUSKBN0JV1H520141218|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

使馆坐落于1977年至2015年间的{{le|美国驻哈瓦那利益代表处|United States Interests Section in Havana}}，代表处在瑞士大使馆的赞助下运作<ref name="state">[http://havana.usint.gov/about-us.html History of the U.S. Interests Section in Cuba.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218023419/http://havana.usint.gov/about-us.html |date=2014-12-18 }} United States Department of State.</ref>。2015年7月1日两国[[古巴解凍|宣布复交]]后，大楼于2015年7月20日恢复美国驻古巴大使馆的作用<ref name="cnne">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/30/politics/u-s-cuba-embassy-relationship/index.html|title=U.S. and Cuba to announce embassy openings|date=2015-06-30|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701070030/http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/30/politics/u-s-cuba-embassy-relationship/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pole">{{cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2015/06/us-and-cuba-to-re-open-embassies-119609.html?hp=l1_3|title=U.S. and Cuba to reopen embassies|date=2015-06-30|publisher=Politico|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702092847/http://www.politico.com/story/2015/06/us-and-cuba-to-re-open-embassies-119609.html?hp=l1_3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reopen">{{cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/afp-us-proposes-us-cuba-reopen-embassies-as-of-july-20-havana-2015-7|title=US proposes US, Cuba reopen embassies as of July 20: Havana|date=2015-07-01|publisher=Business Insider|accessdate=2015-07-20|archive-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905065252/https://www.businessinsider.com/afp-us-proposes-us-cuba-reopen-embassies-as-of-july-20-havana-2015-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
[[File:Havanna_1973_buidling_of_the_former_US_embassy.jpg|thumb]]
大使馆采用建筑公司Harrison & Abramovitz的[[粗野主义|粗野]][[现代主义|现代主义]]设计。大楼为六层混凝土玻璃建筑，于1953年竣工。使馆花园由加利福尼亚州景观设计师{{le|托马斯·多利弗·彻奇|Thomas Dolliver Church}}设计<ref name="state"/>。使馆大楼直接位于{{le|哈瓦那湾|Bay of Havana}}和{{le|何塞·马蒂反帝国主义平台|José Martí Anti-Imperialist Platform}}，靠近{{le|古巴外交部|Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Cuba)}}。

美国外交机构1961年關閉后，该建筑并未被美方人员使用，直至1977年9月1日利益代表处揭幕<ref name="state"/><ref>[http://diplomacy.state.gov/discoverdiplomacy/explorer/places/170222.htm U.S. Interests Section Havana, Cuba.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406030831/http://diplomacy.state.gov/discoverdiplomacy/explorer/places/170222.htm |date=2015-04-06 }} United States Department of State.</ref><ref>[http://graduateinstitute.ch/files/live/sites/iheid/files/sites/international_history_politics/shared/working_papers/WPIHP-Fischer.pdf Talking to the Bearded Man: The Swiss Mandate to Represent U.S. Interests in Cuba, 1961-1977.] {{Wayback|url=http://graduateinstitute.ch/files/live/sites/iheid/files/sites/international_history_politics/shared/working_papers/WPIHP-Fischer.pdf |date=20140729112440 }} Graduate Institute of International and Development Studies.</ref>。1963年，古巴总理[[菲德尔·卡斯特罗|菲德尔·卡斯特罗]]下令没收该大楼，但古巴政府并未采取行动，声称大楼存在有财产权问题<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/18/realestate/cuba-streetscapes-the-new-york-accented-architecture-of-havana.html?_r=0 Havana’s New York Accent.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/18/realestate/cuba-streetscapes-the-new-york-accented-architecture-of-havana.html?_r=0 |date=20170820204114 }} ''New York Times''.</ref>。

在大楼的利益代表处时期，美国由瑞士代表，瑞士保持了使馆大楼及其作用。1997年，大楼完成修缮工作。大楼升级为利益代表处，并于2015年7月20日回归其美国大使馆的原本角色<ref name="cnne"/><ref name="pole"/><ref name="reopen"/>。

目前古巴公民并不能在美国驻古巴大使馆办理美国签证，古巴公民如果要申请签证入境美国则必须前往美国驻其他国家的大使馆或领事馆办理。

